Program: Discovery
Title: Three years after Kyoto
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrxq7
Last Broadcast Date: 17 October 2000
A look at what has happened since the Kyoto agreement on climate change 3 years ago. A commitment to reduce greenhouse gases between 2008 and 2012 was agreed but with so many exclusions, has the Kyoto protocol been successful?